  <p style="max-width:75ch;opacity:.85">
    Certificates of Analysis are provided by third-party laboratories and are
    available by <strong>lot number</strong>. COAs confirm identity, purity,
    and analytical testing of each compound.
  </p>

  <div style="margin:24px 0;padding:16px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:12px;background:#fafafa">
    <strong>How to request a COA</strong>
    <ol style="margin:8px 0 0 18px">
      <li>Locate the lot number printed on your vial label</li>
      <li>Email <strong>coas@vitalfitpeptides.com</strong></li>
      <li>Include the product name and lot number</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

